page.title: 12HOUSING (LAMPHEY)
page.content: Lamphey village itself until recently consisted of only about forty houses. In recent years however a number of housing developments have taken place. These are in the main private housing areas of a relatively expensive nature.Lamphey is a popular area for the professional and management groups as well as retired people. Hodgeston is a small farming village with only a few houses. Freshwater East is a holiday village, there are a number of properties which are occupied all year but there is a large group of properties which are rented out or only occupied for brief periods in the Summer.
